Very short build and installation instructions
==============================================

1) Run from precompiled jar
---------------------------

# tar jxf GoGrid-${VERSION}-jar.tar.bz2

2) Build from source
--------------------

# tar jxf GoGrid-${VERSION}-src.tar.bz2
# cd ant
# ant

Very short running instructions
===============================

# ./Go3DServer.sh &
# ./Go3DClient.sh &
# # etc.